<item>
            <title>[KARAF-143] Setting &quot;karaf.instances&quot; system property has no effect</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KARAF-143</link>
                <project id="12311140" key="KARAF">Karaf</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m trying to separate the static files from the dynamic ones in a karaf deployment but setting the &quot;karaf.instances&quot; system property is ignored (karaf 2.0.0). &lt;br/&gt;
This is because in Main.java on line 191, validate=false when calling Utils.getKarafDirectory(...) so it always revert to the default&lt;/p&gt;</description>
